---
// Demo.astro - Twoja logika + Styl Architect Rounded
---
<section id="demo-section" class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden relative border-t border-slate-100">
  
  <div class="sr-only">
    <h2>Interaktywne Demo Dashboardów – Power BI & JavaScript</h2>
    <p>Przetestuj nasze <strong>usługi Power BI</strong> i raporty online. Dashboardy dla magazynu, sprzedaży i eCommerce.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    
    <header class="max-w-4xl mb-20">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20">
        <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#22c55e]"></span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-green-700">Live Preview</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-[0.95]">
        Kliknij. Sprawdź. <br/>
        <span class="text-green-600 italic">Poczuj różnicę.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Kliknij w miniaturę, aby otworzyć pełnoekranowe, interaktywne demo raportu. Nasze systemy pozwalają na swobodną eksplorację danych w czasie rzeczywistym.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-10 lg:gap-16">
      
      <div
        class="group relative cursor-pointer bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-green-600/10 hover:-translate-y-2 w-full max-w-[540px] flex flex-col"
        role="button"
        tabindex="0"
        @click="openDemo(0)"
        @keydown.enter="openDemo(0)"
        @keydown.space.prevent="openDemo(0)"
      >
        <div class="relative aspect-[16/9] overflow-hidden bg-slate-100">
          <img
            src="/dash1.webp"
            alt="Dashboard Magazyn & Sprzedaż"
            class="object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105 opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/0 group-hover:bg-slate-900/20 transition-all duration-500 flex items-center justify-center">
             <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] flex items-center justify-center scale-90 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-100 transition-all duration-500 shadow-2xl">
                <i class="fas fa-play text-green-600 text-2xl ml-1"></i>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 lg:p-12 border-t border-slate-50 text-center md:text-left">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">Dashboard Magazyn & Sprzedaż</h3>
          <span class="text-sm font-black text-green-600 uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
            Kliknij, aby zobaczyć demo na żywo <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-[10px]"></i>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group relative cursor-pointer bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-green-600/10 hover:-translate-y-2 w-full max-w-[540px] flex flex-col"
        role="button"
        tabindex="0"
        @click="openDemo(1)"
        @keydown.enter="openDemo(1)"
        @keydown.space.prevent="openDemo(1)"
      >
        <div class="relative aspect-[16/9] overflow-hidden bg-slate-100">
          <img
            src="/dash2.webp"
            alt="Dashboard Sprzedaż eCommerce"
            class="object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105 opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/0 group-hover:bg-slate-900/20 transition-all duration-500 flex items-center justify-center">
             <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] flex items-center justify-center scale-90 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-100 transition-all duration-500 shadow-2xl">
                <i class="fas fa-play text-green-600 text-2xl ml-1"></i>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 lg:p-12 border-t border-slate-50 text-center md:text-left">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">Dashboard Sprzedaż eCommerce</h3>
          <span class="text-sm font-black text-green-600 uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
            Kliknij, aby zobaczyć demo na żywo <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-[10px]"></i>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div
  x-cloak
  x-show="showDemo"
  x-transition.opacity
  class="fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur-md"
  @keydown.escape.window="closeDemo()"
>
  <div
    class="bg-white overflow-hidden relative w-full h-full md:w-[96vw] md:h-[94vh] md:rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl"
    @click.outside="closeDemo()"
  >
    <div class="h-16 bg-white border-b border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-between px-8 shrink-0">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="font-black text-slate-900 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Interaktywne Demo Raportu</span>
      </div>
      <button
        type="button"
        @click="closeDemo()"
        class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 hover:bg-red-50 hover:text-red-600 transition-all duration-300"
        aria-label="Zamknij"
      >
        <i class="fas fa-times text-xl"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full h-full bg-slate-50">
      <iframe
        :src="demoSrc"
        class="w-full h-[calc(100%-64px)] border-0 block"
        style="display:block"
        title="Demo dashboardu"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  [x-cloak] { display: none !important; }
</style>